I would like to have the possibility to add content to a main page by label instead of by page title. This is because i want a global page to contain all information (for example: printing a part of system information) and not to have to edit the page every time somebody inserts a new page into the hierarchy.

Before:

{noformat}!foo!bar{noformat}

After round trip:

{noformat}\!foo\!bar{noformat}

