At present confluence does not allow the omission of the username and password when setting up a database in the setup wizard. This prohibits the use of integrated authentication mechanisms provided with drivers such as jtds for SQL server.

We should relax this restriction when we detect that this feature is being used (for example the domain parameter is present in the jtds jdbc url)

