I use the Favourite Pages links on the Dashboard a lot.  However, the order of the labels seems to be fixed: from most recently added at the top to least-recently added at the bottom.  It would be helpful to be able to organize these, like bookmarks in a web browser.  I can see the labels on my User Profile > Personal Labels page, but this page appears to be read-only.  At least an ability to change the order of the links would be helpful.

I suppose the workaround would be to delete and re-add all the links, adding in the reverse order I want to see them listed.  But what a pain.

